<p>The SportAccord Convention offers all delegates the opportunity to listen to leading business figures and renowned athletes from the highest echelons of world sport.  Through inspirational talks and presentations, these high profile individuals share their experiences and insight on global themes shaping  the future of world sport.</p><p>All participants are invited by the host city to enjoy and explore its culture via an extensive, high quality social programme consisting of multiple events and activities across the entire week.</p>